==English==

===Etymology===
1751, from earlier term {{m|en|colloquy|t=a conversation}}, from {{der|en|la|colloquium|t=conference, conversation}}, from {{m|la|con-|t=together}} + {{m|la|loquor|t=to speak}}, + {{af|en|-al}}.

